  "prompt": "Where are the products of Coca-Cola manufactured?",
  "response": "Coca-Cola products are manufactured in various locations around the world. The Coca-Cola Company has a vast network of production facilities, bottling plants, and distribution centers in different countries to meet the global demand for their products. \n\nIn the United States, for example, Coca-Cola operates numerous production facilities across different states. Internationally, the company has production facilities in countries such as Mexico, Brazil, China, India, and many others. \n\nThe exact locations of these facilities can vary over time due to business decisions, expansions, or consolidations. If you're interested in a specific product or region, it might be helpful to check with Coca-Cola's official resources or their website for the most current information.",
